t den Inhalt sinnvoll ab. Die Neuauflage berücksichtigt die zwischenzeitlich ergangene Rechtsprechung und zeichnet wichtige Entwicklungen zum Thema nach.  aInsolvency proceedings are a means by which disadvantageous injunctions against a debtor’s assets can be lifted. This book covers the law governing appeals calling on recent case studies in the Supreme Court.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Aug 2021) 7aLAW / Business & Financial.2bisacsh1 aGehrlein, Markus, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2017z978311071954308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2017z9783110540550oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Law 2017z9783110547771oZDB-23-DGC0 cEPUBz978381455503440uhttps://doi.org/10.15375/978381455792240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783814557922423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783814557922.jpg  a978-3-11-071954-3  DG Plus eBook-Package 2017b2017  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGCb2017  aZDB-23-DGGb2017